I will only launch a fork when I’ve used it sufficiently enough to understand the economics and security model.
That doesn’t mean all of my projects will increase in value forever. It doesn’t mean everything I launch is hacker proof or without flaws. But I will try my damnest to make sure that doens’t happen and we all make it.
To Valhalla!
